snippet.title: The Mobster's Girlfriend: The Story of Amber Brkich - Survivor: All-Stars
snippet.description:
Boston Rob & Amber, an iconic duo that has stood the test of time with their unique alliance that completely dominated and annihilated everyone in their path, but Amber was actually the brains of the operation. So how did Amber do it? Let's find out.

What are the benefits to joining the Patreon for you?
1. You get all of the videos I upload weeks early.
2. You get to pick which Survivor's I tell the stories of for each season of the show.
3. A new Patreon only exclusive video each month.
4. All podcasts are downloadable as MP3's 
5. Your financial support helps the channel to continue and increase the quality and quantity of the videos.
Join today! - https://www.patreon.com/onceuponanislandchannel
